{"tid":337054,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sharp Aquos S2 討論區","createTime":"2017-07-27T03:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T08:08:00.000Z","uid":99908,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e85a84d4750f4aca5dba4dd81221a69994890b","tid":337054,"uid":99908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.gizmochina.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/sharp-aquos-s2-leaked-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmochina.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fsharp-aquos-s2-leaked-01.jpg&h=f3638a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年，手機可以說是迎來了全面屏的大時代，小米、華為、索尼等都推出全面屏手機，而下半年 iPhone 8 也將如約而至，而作為全面屏手機的先行者 Sharp 自然也不甘示弱 , 推出了 第29款全面屏手機 AQUOS S2。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gizmochina.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/sharp-aquos-s2-leaked-04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmochina.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fsharp-aquos-s2-leaked-04.jpg&h=bb838448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n富士康科技集團資深副總裁、Sharp 手機全球 CEO 羅忠生今天在微博宣佈，Sharp 將於 8月8日在北京召開發佈會，正式發布 AQUOS S2 手機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/S1m0IS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FS1m0IS4.png&h=d95cb87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSharp 全面屏新機共有兩款，分高中配版，其中高配版會搭載 Snapdragon 660 處理器，採用解析度為 2040&times;1080 的 5.5吋 IPS LCD 全面屏，提供 6GB RAM + 128GB ROM，配備雙鏡頭， CMOS 為 Sony IMX362。定位中配版的則搭載 Snapdragon 630，同樣配備 5.5吋全面屏，擁有 4GB RAM + 64GB ROM，配備 800萬 +1200萬像素雙鏡頭。此外該新機具備指紋辨識元件、NFC等功能，支援最高 256GB 的 microSD 卡擴展。現預計官方售價高配版價格為 3499元人民幣(約 HK$4050 或 NT$15730 )，中配版價格為 2699元人民幣(約 HK$3120 或 NT$12140 )。"},{"pid":"487705915a3ab8698287f4d38cc72dc886f3bc5b","tid":337054,"uid":99908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OgiJVYP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOgiJVYP.jpg&h=49483a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Hslw6td.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHslw6td.jpg&h=80b811b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eU44V11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeU44V11.jpg&h=c4446194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFront facing camera 同 The Essential Phone 的設計一樣"},{"pid":"023e66b650dacdcadb7332eb75fd00d217957fef","tid":337054,"uid":99908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/48FravD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F48FravD.jpg&h=157f55e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙卡雙4g"},{"pid":"1cd87697a1524441776c7bcfb978000ad41c67a7","tid":337054,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"之前唔係做臭晒個朵咩,仲要賣埋俾富士康都唔慌好得去邊"},{"pid":"769d7eac79d0eb07e1f379994b97a728b69cc73e","tid":337054,"uid":85430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"無知一問，660都係高配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e28140c3c482365a09718ef3dc1f4b9e1fdd207","tid":337054,"uid":99908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.androidheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Sharp-Aquos-S2-leak-12-400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FSharp-Aquos-S2-leak-12-400x400.jpg&h=6ce335bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Bezel-Less&rsquo; Sharp Aquos S2 Leaks Again, This Time In Black<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.androidheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Sharp-Aquos-S2-leak-11-400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FSharp